description:
Sell, buy and swap pre-loved clothes instantly on your phone! List heaps of items FREE and make money from shrinking your closet. Join stylish girls just like you and snatch DEALS on branded pre-loved clothes you’ll adore.

When you download the free Vinted app you dive into an upbeat community of friendly style-savvy girls - Vinties. Join the fun and:

EARN CASH

- Snap a few sweet pics, describe your item - bam! A minute and you’re ready to sell.
- Freedom! Decide how much you make: price the way YOU want.
- Shipping - killing it. Shipping label to track your package through USPS included.
- Transfer your earnings to your bank account, right after the buyer receives her goodies.

SAVE ON TRENDS

- Build your own feed by choosing sizes, following brands and Vinties. Hello there, perfect fit.
- Check out the entirely searchable catalog to find deals on clothes that are right for you.
- Shopping carts? Pff. Chat with sellers directly and know every detail.
- Your money’s safe and YOU DECIDE: tell us you’re happy with what you got or get a refund.

GET INSPIRED! Be yourself and connect with other girls in the forums or through direct messages. DIY, style tips, relationship advice? Yes. Gushing over your favorite actor? Oh God, yes! There’s a fellow Vintie for everything.

Smart wardrobe reinventions, style crushes and new friends happen on Vinted. Word’s already out:

“To all my, Fashionistas! Go download the app, Vinted! You can thank me later(; #BestAppEver” @Ashleyquerfeld

“I am obsessed with this Vinted app. At the rate I'm going, I'll be selling my entire wardrobe.” @ken_z_quinn

“I just bought a pair of boots, studded crossbody purse and knitted beanie all new cond. on VINTED for only $35” @TLeeLavish

“I love the Vinted app! Bought so many cute things alreadyyy #addicted #shopaholic” @irenekngo

“Literally posted this dress an hour ago and sold it on the #vinted app 5 minutes ago!!!!” @SumKindaWndrful


Share the joy with so many other girls who are crazy about Vinted on Twitter! Don’t miss out and download now - it’s FREE and we’d love to meet you.

Check us out if you like Poshmark, Threadflip or other peer-to-peer clothing marketplaces.

* We work hard to improve the app and delight our members with great functionality. If you have feedback, we want to know! Give us a shout at hello@vinted.com *
releaseNotes: Once upon a time there was a pesky bug that prevented Vinties from seeing photos in full screen. But along came the Vinted fairies and vanquished the bug with a twiddle of their magic wands! And they all lived happily ever bug-free after
